âœ… Volume-mounted ConfigMaps: Preserved when used by pods
âœ… Environment Variable ConfigMaps: Preserved when referenced in env
âœ… EnvFrom ConfigMaps: Preserved when used in envFrom blocks
âœ… Init Container ConfigMaps: Preserved when used by init containers
âœ… Protected ConfigMaps: Respects cleanup.kyverno.io/exclude: "true" annotation
âœ… System Namespaces: Excludes kube-system, kube-public, etc.
âœ… Report Generation: Verifies audit and usage reports are created

